column5: Super day on the water with incredible weather.  Guides froze every other cast till the sun came out to play.  After trying this one spot a dozen times, i added an ab splitshot and got a hit instantly.  Fished first light till noon.   Sunny and clear conditions made for fussy fishing.  25"  18" female
always great to see your reports maing!!! glad you had a fantastic day! Taker EZ Andrew
nice chrome man! im hoping to get out in the morning, ill make sure to bring some vasoline to keep the guides ice free
Congrats on the nice trout, it was a beautiful if crisp morning around here.  Drifting roe?  Mike
Nice fish man i bet u had the river to your self on a tuesday i wish i could get out as much as u.    jordan
nice report & pics,those fish are so silver.....
Good report.  We should fish together soon...  DAVE
